  <entry>
    <title>3/17 纯粹容器会做悲伤的梦吗</title>
    <link href="https://tototofoo.github.io/blog/2021/03/17/3-15/"/>
    <id>https://tototofoo.github.io/blog/2021/03/17/3-15/</id>
    <published>2021-03-17T03:57:37.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-03-17T05:51:15.086Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/blog/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/blog/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>图太大了传不上就直接放链接好了</p><p>​<a id="more"></a></p><h2 id="漫画"><a class="header-anchor" href="#漫画">☆</a>漫画</h2><p><a href="https://uxddd.lofter.com/post/1cae1417_1cbbc0766" target="_blank" rel="noopener">全览</a></p><h2 id="附带杂谈"><a class="header-anchor" href="#附带杂谈">☆</a>附带杂谈</h2>        <div id="aplayer-oTnLEfVh" class="aplayer aplayer-tag-marker" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">            <pre class="aplayer-lrc-content"></pre>        </div>        <script>          var ap = new APlayer({            element: document.getElementById("aplayer-oTnLEfVh"),            narrow: false,            autoplay: false,            showlrc: false,            music: {              title: "Enter Hallownest",              author: "Christopher Larkin",              url: "http://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=1309394487.mp3",              pic: "",              lrc: ""            }          });          window.aplayers || (window.aplayers = []);          window.aplayers.push(ap);        </script><p>​是突发画的同人漫画, 缘由是第一次戴耳机认真听了HK的bgm, 实在是大受感动…</p><p>​(是音乐源动力型人了)</p><p>​虽然没玩过魂系列的游戏, 但似乎这类游戏的剧情都埋的相当隐晦, 从小就开始玩横版2d的我对这种好感度还是加成很高的. 跑白宫那张地图的时候因为注意力都在过电锯上面, 满脑子都是滋儿哇, 后来单独去听里面的音乐才发现原来这么精妙.</p><p>​能够构建完整的一个世界, 虽然打的时候感觉npc有点谜语人, 但耐不住boss战实在是太棒了.</p><p>​画的有点长还是有点累, 好歹画完了…! (明明说不想画条漫但还是, 我身体好正直)</p><p>​屑沃姆的叉子头再也不想画了!!!</p>]]></content>
    
    
